---
// IntroSection component
---

<section class="scroll-section intro-section" id="intro" data-section="intro">
  <div class="intro-container">
    <!-- intro 文字 (左側) -->
    <div class="intro-left">
      <div class="intro-text-stack">
        <h2 class="intro-title">intro</h2>
        <h2 class="intro-title">intro</h2>
        <h2 class="intro-title">intro</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- 圓圈區域 (右側) -->
    <div class="intro-right">
      <div class="circles-container">
        <div class="circle circle-inner">
          <div class="circle-content">
            <h3 class="circle-heading">致力成為世界一流的製造服務整合者與持續成長的永續經營企業</h3>
            <p class="circle-description">
              聚焦擁有創新管理思維、專業素養及技術能量、進件客戶佈局、
              創新設計研發、全球資訊整合，市場細緻分析等多項能力，從聚
              集成為台灣最式界領航者，亦展美、日、歐、台各大服飾品牌與
              零售業者主要合作夥伴，在全球皮革產業價值鏈中取得關鍵地
              位。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .scroll-section {
    position: relative;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .intro-section {
    background: #C39270;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .intro-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    height: 100vh;
    padding: 0 0 0 6rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .intro-left {
    color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
    font-size: 220px;
    line-height: 220px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    z-index: 5;
    font-family: Boska-Medium;
    position: absolute;
    left: -300px;
    top: 45%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }

  .intro-right {
    flex: 2;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    height: 100vh;
    position: relative;
  }

  .circles-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .intro-text-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: -2rem;
  }

  .intro-title {
    font-weight: 100;
    text-transform: lowercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  /* 漸變效果 */

  .intro-title:nth-child(2) {
    margin-left: 2rem;
    //opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .intro-title:nth-child(3) {
    margin-left: 4rem;
    //opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .circle {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .circle-inner {
    width: 100vh;
    height: 100vh;
    background: #E8E8E8;
    border: none;
    padding: 3rem;
    z-index: 3;
    position: relative;
  }

  .circle-inner::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 115vh;
    height: 115vh;
    background: #F1D5C7;
    border-radius: 50%;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .circle-inner::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 130vh;
    height: 130vh;
    background: #F9B48F;
    border-radius: 50%;
    z-index: -2;
  }

  .circle-content {
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
    background: #E8E8E8;
    border-radius: 50%;
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .circle-heading {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2d3436;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .circle-description {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #636e72;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(5deg);
    }
  }

  /* 響應式設計 */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .intro-container {
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .intro-left {
      z-index: 10;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .intro-title {
      font-size: 6rem;
    }

    .intro-right {
      flex: 1;
      height: 60vh;
    }

    .circle-outer {
      width: 80vw;
      height: 80vw;
    }

    .circle-middle {
      width: 65vw;
      height: 65vw;
    }

    .circle-inner {
      width: 50vw;
      height: 50vw;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .circle-heading {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .circle-description {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  }
</style>
